OL,5, British pop singer Matty Healy's       
OL,6, protest stunt at a concert in Malaysia 
OL,7, has sparked fury from LGBT activists   
OL,8, and allies in the country.             
OL,10,FMany have described the 1975 singer's  
OL,11,Fsweary rant at the Malaysian government
OL,12,F- and kiss with a male bandmate - as an
OL,13,Fact of "performative activism" that    
OL,14,Fwould make their lives even harder.    
OL,17,FIn a statement after Friday's show, a  
OL,18,Fsource close to the band said Healy had
OL,19,Fwanted to stand up for the LGBT        
OL,20,Fcommunity.                             
